2-4 fillets of Mahi Mahi Tuna
Handful of Dried Whole Prunes
Sim. Pecans
Sim. Apricots
1/2 cup of red wine
1/2 cup of Mojo with a good amount of the garlic (see Mixtoes)
Tbs of Mojo (just the oil)
Salt to taste

Sauce: rough chop the fruits and nuts. In a small sauce pan on medium, pring to a slow boild with the lrg. Mojo and the wine. Render on medium until desired consistency.

salt the fillets and drizzle a hot skillet with the sm. Mojo oil. Cook 4 minutes on each side. Plate when done and sfruit sauce atop. Hit with pepper and parsley.

